      <scopecontent id="aspace_15ad023c6b7d60cd58dcb6e2002c6b2d">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection comprises correspondence, scrapbooks, photographs, prints, drawings, and publications concerning Hubert von Herkomer, and Herkomer's family.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
